<div class='media__message'>
<h4 class='h12 talk-link__speaker'>Angela Lee Duckworth</h4>
<h4 class='h9 m5'>
<a class='' href='http://www.ted.com/talks/1733?language=en' lang='en'>
The key to success? Grit
</a>
</h4>
<div class='meta'>
<span class='meta__item'>
Posted
<span class='meta__val'>
May 2013
</span>
</span>
<span class='meta__row'>
Rated
<span class='meta__val'>
Inspiring, Informative
</span>
</span>
